OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry night
OL,6,Fwith clear spells, and overnight
OL,7,Ftemperatures rather fresher than of
OL,8,Flate especially in rural spots. One or
OL,9,Ftwo mist or fog patches developing in
OL,10,Fprone areas. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry with hazy sunshine and
OL,13,Fvery warm for many again on Saturday.
OL,14,FCloud thickening somewhat overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FTurning
OL,17,Fmore unsettled and cooler into the
OL,18,Fstart of next week. Temperatures
OL,19,Ffalling nearer normal for the time of
OL,20,Fyear. Becoming breezy with outbreaks
OL,21,Fof occasionally heavy rain or showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
